reviewText: Avoid this DVD!  For example, on the English part there are 2 portions.  All on the Kew Garden.  Mind, I like gardens as much as the next person, but all devoted to a tiered presentation of the Kew Garden.  Not good.

The scenery is beautiful but the woman's voice is annoying and the music does not suit the video. LOUD jazzy music playing (louder than the narrator) while talking about a church or meadow. Background music is fine but this was awful.
